<div class="colhead"><h6>FAQ</h6></div>

<div id="artbody" class="artblock">
	

    
        
            <h5>Contact Us</h5>
        
        
	
        
        
            <p><b><a href="#faq1">How can I contact the author of an article?</a><br /><a href="#faq2">How frequently do you update the site?</a><br /><a href="#faq27">I have an idea for New Scientist.</a></b></p>
        
	
        
            <h5>Website - Premium Content</h5>
        
        
	
        
        
            <p><b><a href="#faq4">How do I get access to Premium Content?</a><br /><a href="#faq5">What is Premium Content?</a><br /><a href="#faq6">Why can't I access Premium Content?</a><br /><a href="#faq29">I have forgotten my username and password</a><br /><a href="#faq30">Can I subscribe to Premium Content and not the magazine?</a><br /><a href="#faq31">Why have you started charging for content?</a></b></p>
        
	
        
            <h5>Other website questions</h5>
        
        
	
        
        
            <p><b><a href="#faq28">Where is books/feedback/lastword/letters/weblinks?</a><br /><a href="#faq3">Where has the Archive gone?</a><br /><a href="#faq7">How do I search NewScientist.com?</a><br /><a href="#faq8">The graphics are too small to see properly.</a><br /><a href="#faq9">I can't find the article I'm looking for.</a><br /><a href="#faq10">Is there a subscription fee for your website? Do you have to register to use it?</a><br /><a href="#faq11">Are you going to produce a mobile version of the site?</a><br /><a href="#faq12">How do I subscribe to the electronic newsletter?</a><br /><a href="#faq13">How do I unsubscribe from the electronic newsletter?</a></b></p>
        
	
        
            <h5>Back Issues</h5>
        
        
	
        
        
